'''FormatFactory''' is an [[Adware|ad-supported]] freeware multimedia converter that can convert video, audio, and picture files. It is also capable of ripping DVDs and CDs to other file formats, as well as creating [[.iso]] images. It can also join multiple video files together into one.{{Citation needed|date=February 2010}} FormatFactory supports the following formats:
